snippet.title: Probability 0 Trailer
snippet.description:
Probability 0
is its own kind of infinite arcade platformer shmup thing in which you dodge stuff, shoot stuff, learn new stuff, punch stuff, and die a lot.

http://www.droqen.com/probability0.html

Also, the music of Probability 0 was made by JMickle. The soundtrack was released as of January 2013! IT'S HERE:

http://jmickle.bandcamp.com/album/probability-zero
